==Swedish==
===Etymology===
The word is originally a short form for ''Månens dag'', meaning ''day of the [[w:Moon|Moon]]''. 

===Noun===
'''måndag''' ''c'' (''plural'' [[måndagar]], ''definite singular'' [[måndagen]], ''definite plural'' [[måndagarna]])

# [[Monday]]. The first day of the [[week]] (according to the [[ISO]] 8601 [[standard]]).

